---
import { ShieldCheck } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section class="py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      
      <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 mb-8 mx-auto">
        <ShieldCheck className="w-8 h-8" />
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6">Engineered for Performance.</h2>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-12 leading-relaxed">
        Because we follow a strict framework, our results are predictable. We don't guess. <br class="hidden md:block">
        If we accept you as a partner, itâ€™s because our data shows we can grow your clinic.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-left bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand"></span>
            Exclusivity
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm pl-4 border-l-2 border-slate-200">
            We only work with one clinic per radius for specific niches to avoid conflict of interest. We don't play both sides.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-2">
           <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand"></span>
            Transparency
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm pl-4 border-l-2 border-slate-200">
            You own your data, your ad accounts, and your creative assets. Always. No hostage situations.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
